## Typography Requirements

### Font Hierarchy by Brand

| Brand | Primary Font | Fallback | Weights Required | Where to Use |
|-------|--------------|----------|------------------|--------------|
| Toyota | Toyota Type | Helvetica Neue | Regular, Medium, Bold | Headers, body, CTAs |
| Honda | Honda Sans | Arial | Regular, Bold | All text |
| Ford | Antenna | Arial | Regular, Medium, Bold | Headers, body |
| Chevrolet | Louis | Helvetica Neue | Regular, Bold, Heavy | Headers, body |
| BMW | BMW Helvetica | Helvetica | Light, Regular, Bold | All text |
| Mercedes | Corporate A | Helvetica | Regular, Bold | Headers, body |
| Nissan | Nissan Brand | Arial | Light, Regular, Bold | All text |
| Hyundai | Hyundai Sans | Helvetica | Regular, Medium, Bold | All text |
| VW | VW Head | DIN | Regular, Bold | Headers, body |
| Mazda | Mazda Type | Frutiger | Regular, Bold | All text |
| Subaru | Subaru | Futura | Book, Medium, Bold | All text |
| Kia | Kia Signature | Helvetica | Regular, Bold | All text |
| Lexus | Lexus | Helvetica Neue | Light, Regular, Bold | All text |
| Acura | Acura | Gotham | Book, Medium, Bold | All text |
| Audi | Audi Type | Helvetica | Normal, Bold | All text |

### Font Loading Strategy

```javascript
// For licensed fonts (Toyota Type, BMW Helvetica, etc.)
// Load from brand's official CDN or use fallback

const brandFonts = {
  toyota: {
    primary: '"Toyota Type", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif',
    cdn: 'https://www.toyota.com/fonts/toyota-type.css'
  },
  honda: {
    primary: '"Honda Sans", Arial, sans-serif',
    cdn: null // Use fallback
  },
  // ... etc
};
```

---

## Logo Usage Rules

### Logo Specifications

| Brand | Clear Space | Min Size Web | Min Size Print | File Formats |
|-------|-------------|--------------|----------------|--------------|
| Toyota | 1x logo height | 100px width | 0.5 inch | SVG, PNG |
| Honda | 0.5x logo width | 80px width | 0.4 inch | SVG, PNG |
| Ford | Logo height | 120px width | 0.6 inch | SVG, PNG |
| Chevrolet | 0.75x logo width | 90px width | 0.5 inch | SVG, PNG |
| BMW | Logo diameter | 100px width | 0.5 inch | SVG, PNG |
| Mercedes | 1x star width | 100px width | 0.5 inch | SVG, PNG |

### Logo Color Variations

**All brands provide:**
- ✅ Full color version (primary)
- ✅ Monochrome black
- ✅ Monochrome white (for dark backgrounds)
- ❌ Do NOT create custom colored versions

### Logo Don'ts (Universal)

❌ **Never:**
- Stretch or distort logo
- Change logo colors
- Add effects (shadows, gradients)
- Rotate logo
- Place on busy backgrounds
- Use low-resolution versions

---

## Design Standards

### Button Styles by Brand

#### Primary CTA Buttons

| Brand | Background | Text | Hover | Border |
|-------|------------|------|-------|--------|
| Toyota | `#EB0A1E` (red) | White | `#CC0000` | None |
| Honda | `#CC0000` (red) | White | `#A00000` | None |
| Ford | `#003478` (blue) | White | `#0076CE` | None |
| Chevrolet | `#FFC72C` (gold) | Black | `#FFD75E` | None |
| BMW | `#1C69D4` (blue) | White | `#3E8BE0` | None |
| Mercedes | `#000000` (black) | White | `#4D4D4D` | 1px white |
| Nissan | `#C3002F` (red) | White | `#A00027` | None |
| Hyundai | `#002C5F` (blue) | White | `#0E4C92` | None |

#### Secondary Buttons

- Background: White or Light Gray
- Border: Brand primary color
- Text: Brand primary color
- Hover: Brand primary color background with white text

### Header Styles

**All brands require:**
- ✅ Logo in top left or center
- ✅ Navigation in brand colors
- ✅ Contact info visible
- ✅ Mobile-responsive menu
- ❌ No competing logos or branding

### Footer Requirements

**Must include:**
- ✅ Brand logo
- ✅ Dealership contact info
- ✅ Legal disclaimers
- ✅ Privacy policy link
- ✅ Manufacturer website link
- ❌ No competitor logos

---

## Implementation Guide

### CSS Color Variables

```css
/* Toyota Example */
:root {
  /* Primary Colors */
  --toyota-red: #EB0A1E;
  --toyota-black: #000000;
  --toyota-white: #FFFFFF;
  
  /* Secondary Colors */
  --toyota-gray: #58595B;
  --toyota-light-gray: #F7F7F7;
  --toyota-dark-red: #CC0000;
  
  /* Application */
  --brand-primary: var(--toyota-red);
  --brand-text: var(--toyota-black);
  --brand-background: var(--toyota-white);
  --brand-accent: var(--toyota-gray);
}

/* Buttons */
.btn-primary {
  background-color: var(--brand-primary);
  color: var(--brand-background);
  border: none;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  background-color: var(--toyota-dark-red);
}
```

### React/TypeScript Implementation

```typescript
// brandColors.ts
export const brandColors = {
  toyota: {
    primary: '#EB0A1E',
    secondary: '#000000',
    background: '#FFFFFF',
    accent: '#58595B',
    lightGray: '#F7F7F7',
    hover: '#CC0000'
  },
  honda: {
    primary: '#CC0000',
    secondary: '#0047BB',
    background: '#FFFFFF',
    accent: '#BABCBE',
    lightGray: '#F5F5F5',
    hover: '#A00000'
  },
  ford: {
    primary: '#003478',
    secondary: '#000000',
    background: '#FFFFFF',
    accent: '#6C6E70',
    lightGray: '#E5E5E5',
    hover: '#0076CE'
  },
  // ... all other brands
};

// Usage in component
import { brandColors } from './brandColors';

const DealerWebsite = ({ brand }: { brand: string }) => {
  const colors = brandColors[brand.toLowerCase()] || brandColors.toyota;
  
  return (
    <div style={{ backgroundColor: colors.background }}>
      <button style={{
        backgroundColor: colors.primary,
        color: colors.background
      }}>
        Schedule Test Drive
      </button>
    </div>
  );
};
```

### Validation Checklist

Before launching dealer website, verify:

**Colors:**
- [ ] Primary brand color used for all CTAs
- [ ] Secondary colors used appropriately
- [ ] No unauthorized colors used
- [ ] Hover states match brand guidelines
- [ ] Backgrounds are brand-compliant

**Typography:**
- [ ] Brand font loaded or fallback used
- [ ] Font weights are correct
- [ ] Text hierarchy follows brand standards

**Logo:**
- [ ] Official logo used (not modified)
- [ ] Correct clear space maintained
- [ ] Minimum size requirements met
- [ ] Proper color version used

**Layout:**
- [ ] Professional, brand-appropriate design
- [ ] Mobile-responsive
- [ ] Fast loading
- [ ] Accessible (WCAG 2.1 AA)

