## Summary

This document provides exact specifications for all major automotive brands. Our system uses these exact colors and standards to ensure every dealer website is:

✅ **Brand Compliant** - Follows official manufacturer guidelines  
✅ **Professional** - Looks premium and trustworthy  
✅ **Consistent** - Matches brand identity across all touchpoints  
✅ **Legal** - Meets contractual requirements for authorized dealers  

**For Development Team:**
- Use exact HEX codes provided
- Load brand fonts or use fallbacks
- Validate against this document before launch
- Update when brands release new guidelines

**For Dealers:**
- Trust the system to apply correct branding
- No customization of brand colors allowed
- Compliance is automatic
- Manufacturer approval built-in
